snippet.title: Defunct Launch Trailer Youtube
snippet.description:
Do you feel it? The need for Speed? If so, then start your gravitation engine and engage your thrusters. Indie racing-adventure; Defunct, is out now and your mothership is already leaving the planet! So set of in hot pursuit and traverse 11 varied levels full of different climates, biomes and challenges. Done with that? Then you can unlock 5 skins, 5 tricks and compete for the best completion times 5 exclusive time trail mode levels.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/359350
